(1473, 1, '2016-02-20 19:09:43', '2016-02-20 19:09:43', '[gallery masterslider="false" size="full" thumbs="false" caption="false" ids="2025,2024,2023"]\n\n<strong>Welcome, step inside and take a seat .</strong>.. actually before you sit down, let me show you around. This is our new Envato headquarters in Melbourne, Australia. Situated in Melbourne’s central business district, on King St, home to a weird mix of big corporate buildings, delicious Japanese food and *ahem* gentlemen''s clubs!\n\n<!--more-->\n\nBefore we moved in, this three story heritage building was used as a school. Going back even further, the building was a storage facility for Ferguson''s Winery. Now there’s less wine and more developers, computer screens and agile boards.\n\nhttp://inside.envato.com/envato-office-tour/\n\n<em>Photos by <a href="http://marmaras.com/">John Marmaras</a>, <a href="http://www.devikabilimoria.com/">Devika Bilimoria</a> and <a href="https://twitter.com/joshjanssen">Josh Janssen</a>.</em>', 'Tour of Envato''s Melbourne Headquarters', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tour-of-envatos-melbourne-headquarters', '', '', '2016-02-20 19:09:43', '2016-02-20 19:09:43', '', 0, 'http://themes.temashdesign.com/woodstock/electronics/?p=1473', 0, 'post', '', 0),
